('93', 'MINIATURE CRESTED COATL', 'Golden Cave', 'Small', 'Gold', '1 egg', 'Playful', 'From  a distance, this coatl is often mistaken for I a bird. Only up close can it be observed that the dragon is scaled instead of feathered, from the tip of its nose to its distinctive tail scales.', 'img/DragonPics/93.jpg'), 
